\layout Itemize

A new approach to detect myocardial ischemia (lack of oxygen in one's heart)
 was proposed 
\begin_inset LatexCommand \cite{key-59}

\end_inset 


\begin_inset LatexCommand \cite{key-62}

\end_inset 

